## Input

```css
.test {
  label:hover {
    color: red;
  }

  font:bold {
    color: blue;
  }

  font:12px {
    family: sans-serif;
  }

  font: bold {
    family: serif;
  }

  #{$name}:hover {
    color: green;
  }

  a:#{$pseudo} {
    color: teal;
  }

  font-#{$weight}:bold {
    color: purple;
  }

  font-#{$weight}::before {
    color: orange;
  }
}

